# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
# Libraries should not commit pubspec.lock, per https://dart.dev/guides/libraries/private-files#pubspeclock.
**/pubspec.lock
**/doc/api/
**/.dart_tool/
**/.flutter-plugins
**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/.metadata
/build/
**/build/
# Exception: DevTools extension web build must be committed so pub.dev can serve it.
!packages/hyper_render_devtools/extension/devtools/build/
!packages/hyper_render_devtools/extension/devtools/build/**
/coverage/

# Publish preparation (temporary file generated by scripts/publish.sh)
pubspec_publish_ready.yaml

# CI pipeline artifacts (uploaded to GitHub Actions, not for VCS)
analyze_report.txt
benchmark/results/

# Golden test failure artifacts (auto-generated by flutter test, not for VCS)
test/golden/failures/

# Local working notes — review responses, decision drafts, scratch analyses.
# Belong in conversation / PR descriptions, not in the published library.
# (Note: top-level `docs/` was removed in v1.3.2 — pub.dev convention is `doc/`.
# Internal-only review notes live in `doc/internal/` which is gitignored above.)
*.scratch.md
